                  <additions>There are several marginal notes, frequently erased, in a later (probably sixteenth-century) hand, seemingly by a critic. 
                     At the foot of fol. 1v is a sixteenth-century note: 'This booke was compiled by Reynolde pecocke, bisshope of Asaphensis and after Bysshopin of Cicestrensis, 
                     anno domini 1457'. (NB: this date is not correct.)
